name: Knockout
Poison
note:
<Negative State>
<JS Slip Refresh>

<JS HP Slip Damage>
const elementID = 12;
if (target.getAbsorbedElements().contains(elementID)) {
  var healing = 2 * user.mat;
  target.gainHp(healing);
  target.startDamagePopup();
} else {
  damage = Math.floor(2 * user.mat * target.elementRate(elementID));
};
</JS HP Slip Damage>

<JS On Add State>
target.setFaceImage(target._faceName, 3);
</JS On Add State>

<JS On Erase State>
if (target._states.length == 0) {
target.setFaceImage(target._faceName, 0);
};
</JS On Erase State>

<JS On Expire State>

target.setFaceImage(target._faceName, 0);
};
</JS On Expire State>

name: Low Health
note:
<Negative State>

<JS Passive Condition>
if (user.hpRate() <= 0.25) {
  if (user._faceName != null) {
    user.setFaceImage(user._faceName, 2);
  };
  condition = true;
} else {
  if (user._states.length == 0) {
    if (user._faceName != null) {
      user.setFaceImage(user._faceName, 0);
    };
  };
  condition = false;
};
</JS Passive Condition>
